commentable_entity.description: Amber Heard was married to Johnny Depp. Right now there is a court case against her from him. Lies she said about him raping her beating her and other things. In videos and conversations between them too is alarming. Amber Heard had a daughter and I'm highly concerned about the welfare of her child. Amber has been known in the past to abuse her partners. She has a history of drug abuse and alcohol abuse. She is very unstable and needs to be investigated if she is still using and unstable. As of now amber has been lying on the stand in court. I am very concerned for her daughter and I want social services to fully investigate Amber as a mother. I have seen many people concerned about this as well. I'm hoping starting a petition will get the proper people to look further into her private life with her daughter. Please sign
